definitions.definition: The chores of maintaining a house as a residence, especially cleaning.
Any general tasks that involve preparation.
examples: The computer program does some general housekeeping involving initializing variables and opening files before beginning the main processing.

definitions.definition: Announcements that must be made before a show or event can begin.
examples: Thank you all for coming! Just some quick housekeeping before we get underway, the emergency exits are to your left...

definitions.definition: Hospitality; a liberal and hospitable table; a supply of provisions.
